Trading in shares of SchweizerischeAluminium AG, Alusuisse, &lt;ALUZ.Z> was suspended on the Zurichstock exchange after today's announcement by the company thatit would cut its share capital by 50 pct, the bourse said.    The bourse said trading would resume again on Monday.    Alusuisse bearer shares closed at 490 francs yesterday,registered shares at 170 francs and the participationcertificates at 45.50. REUTER&#3;